title: The Bubble (Ha-Buah) 2006 OST
description:
Ha-Buah (The Bubble), the 2006 film's original soundtrack. My apologies if the quality of the songs varies. I spent hours searching for this album and I couldn't find it anywhere, so I had to download each song one by one. Here's the track list: 

1. Bright Eyes - First Day Of My Life 
2. Nada Surf - Always Love 
3. Lloyd Cole - Music In A Foreign Language 
4. Keren Ann - Chelsea Burns 
5. Ivri Lider - The Man I Love 
6. Belle & Sebastian - Woman's Realm 
7. Acid House Kings - Tonight Is Forever 
8. Amit Erez - Clever and Strong 
9. Jay Walk Snail - Holly Scott and the Aerial 
10. Keren Ann - Sit In the Sun 
11. Antiquex - Day Out / Close To You 
12. Ivry Lider - Birthday Cake 
13. Ivri Lider - Song To A Siren
